{"date":"1986-03-01","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/87/2d/4213_DyKAz.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/87/2d/4213_DyKAz.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/87/2d/4213_DyKAz.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/87/2d/4213_DyKAz.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/87/2d/4213_DyKAz.jpg"},"summary":"宇宙世纪0088年，经过格利普斯战役，提坦兹（Titans）被消灭，奥古（AEUG）的实力也大大削弱。吉恩军残余部队在摄政王哈曼・坎恩的率领下趁机以“新吉恩”的名义称霸地球。\r\n在格利普斯战役中受损的奥古军宇宙战舰“阿伽马号”临时停靠在Side1的殖民卫星“香格里拉”。此地经营废品回收业务的捷度・阿西塔和朋友们盯上了阿伽马内的Z高达，准备偷出来卖钱。恰好此时与阿伽马敌对的新吉恩军巡洋舰“安多拉号”也来到了香格里拉，捷度等人被卷入了战斗。","name":"機動戦士ガンダムΖΖ","name_cn":"机动战士高达ZZ","tags":[{"name":"高达","count":580,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":438,"total_cont":0},{"name":"富野由悠季","count":416,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":387,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1986","count":296,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":263,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":209,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GUNDAM","count":169,"total_cont":0},{"name":"哈曼SAMA","count":116,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ZZ","count":105,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":91,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":87,"total_cont":0},{"name":"前半搞笑","count":85,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":59,"total_cont":0},{"name":"アニメじゃない！","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"妹控必看","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战争","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补旧番","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980s","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1986年3月","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"北爪宏幸","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大波ZETA","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"年番","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1986年","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"UC","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":5,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"机动战士高达ZZ"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"機動戦士ガンダ